### onRowDataUpdated

```typescript
/**
 * Client-Side Row Model only. The client has updated data for the grid by either a) setting new Row Data or b) Applying a Row Transaction.
 * 
 */
(event: RowDataUpdatedEvent<TData>) => void
```

